#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:2 5d82079bc6b14c2f8075d9b3b8ed4509
msgid "M5UI"
msgstr "M5UI"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:7 fb32a43371644f3b947ff36893ab6c26
msgid ""
"M5UI is a UI library based on LVGL v9.3. It provides a set of widgets and"
" functions to create user interfaces for M5Stack devices."
msgstr "M5UI 是一个基于 LVGL v9.3 的 UI 库。它提供了一组用于创建 M5Stack 设备用户界面的小部件和函数。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:9 c9d117566a6e4809bbd3cbaaa0496675
msgid ""
"It has been adapted for M5Stack devices and you only need to call "
"``m5ui.init()`` to start using it."
msgstr "它已适用于 M5Stack 设备，您只需调用 ``m5ui.init()`` 即可开始使用它。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:12 defd0685ca05486f8a4820c7825d221c
msgid "M5 Series Display Libraries"
msgstr "M5 系列显示库说明"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:15 73f56f479c3c4ca0be68f6ab5634649c
#, fuzzy
msgid "1. Display (M5.Lcd)"
msgstr "显示"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:16 a471f7acadf74cc997ba59b23ddeab07
msgid ""
"A low-level graphics library providing basic screen drawing, text, lines,"
" and color management."
msgstr "底层图形库，提供屏幕绘制、文字、线条、颜色管理等基础功能。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:17 5044ae14710840a180a091ef63509bec
msgid ""
"Can be used independently, suitable for scenarios that only require "
"drawing graphics or text."
msgstr "可独立使用，适合只需要绘制图形或文字的场景。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:18 6b7327413a7147ba95ccbceb9bd362b8
msgid ""
"**Access via**: ``M5.Lcd.fillRect()``, ``M5.Lcd.drawRect()``, "
"``M5.Lcd.drawString()``, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:21 699934bf5bef44d9a51c6c0d0405d265
#, fuzzy
msgid "2. Widgets (M5.Widgets)"
msgstr "2. 控件"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:22 6e28083fa1064537880f9846d34fbf82
msgid ""
"A basic UI widget library providing labels, image displays, and other UI "
"controls."
msgstr "基础控件库，提供标签、图片显示等 UI 控件。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:23 08f2007ddaab4a81806e84af51524890
msgid "Built on top of M5GFX."
msgstr "底层依赖 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:24 ccaa93465d0443be83923985d7a80a36
msgid "Suitable for simple interactive UI elements."
msgstr "适合需要简单交互控件的界面。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:25 64fe79967cdf4e40acc4b99724a7c945
msgid ""
"**Access via**: ``M5.Widgets.Label()``, ``M5.Widgets.Image()``, "
"``M5.Widgets.Rectangle()``, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:26 22e76dc27819415da6c900a70a88d2a8
msgid ""
"**Important**: ``M5.Widgets`` provides UI component **classes**, not "
"drawing methods."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:29 6f72bbc6090e4b6390c0f1dddbd90e4a
msgid "3. M5UI"
msgstr "3. M5UI"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:30 eb217851d5cb4a9d8bf33bd13babb8a1
msgid "A high-level UI framework based on LVGL."
msgstr "高层 UI 框架，基于 LVGL 封装。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:31 6dbdbbeb472d4c7aa6a1595e1d9c22ee
msgid ""
"Provides page management, multi-widget layouts, and unified event "
"handling."
msgstr "提供页面管理、多控件布局和统一事件处理。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:32 6626d2c4abbe47c0963e1ffd024a67bd
msgid ""
"**Access via**: ``m5ui.M5Label()``, ``m5ui.M5Button()``, "
"``m5ui.M5Page()``, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:35 b1d3c2ed64d142a6bf9d13d9886669b2
msgid "Usage Tips"
msgstr "使用提示"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:36 f8a359c0b8e6498496ef3f96ae84bde5
msgid ""
"⚠️ Do not mix M5GFX, M5Widgets, and M5UI simultaneously, as it may cause "
"rendering issues or event conflicts."
msgstr "⚠️ 不建议同时混用 M5GFX、M5Widgets、M5UI，可能导致渲染异常或事件冲突。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:37 8c839e1ae88f4067bdcb000cecae02b1
#, fuzzy
msgid "For graphics-only drawing → use M5GFX (M5.Lcd)."
msgstr "单独绘图 → 使用 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:38 bfaa19ad316b480e92a810226babf69a
msgid "For simple interactive widgets → use M5Widgets."
msgstr "简单控件交互 → 使用 M5Widgets。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:39 fdfb721395a648909e708a7b673087a3
msgid "For multi-page UI → use M5UI."
msgstr "多页面 UI → 使用 M5UI。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:42 3ddbbfbc7484424b988afe5489f3b6a4
msgid "Common Mistakes to Avoid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:43 b236050a18804cc6b83d86bfdc7e6231
msgid ""
"❌ **WRONG**: ``Widgets.fillRect()`` or ``Widgets.drawRect()`` - These "
"methods do not exist in Widgets module"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:44 a34a0fc7e19d4615a65efc72f22e9f7d
msgid ""
"✅ **CORRECT**: ``M5.Lcd.fillRect()`` or ``M5.Lcd.drawRect()`` - Use "
"M5.Lcd for drawing methods"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:45 808173fb8c524d68ba8666f0eba5416d
msgid ""
"❌ **WRONG**: Mixing ``M5.Widgets.Rectangle()`` with ``m5ui.M5Page()`` - "
"Different UI systems, don't mix"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:46 70788de32cf0426c8efdd52397121668
msgid ""
"✅ **CORRECT**: Use either M5.Widgets OR m5ui consistently, not both "
"together"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:48 3011c644b812463c81b4c2a2d0fabfce
msgid ""
"**Key Distinction**: - ``M5.Lcd`` = Drawing methods (fillRect, drawRect, "
"drawCircle, drawString, etc.) - ``M5.Widgets`` = Simple UI component "
"classes (Label, Image, Rectangle, Circle, etc.) - ``m5ui`` = LVGL-based "
"UI framework (M5Label, M5Button, M5Page, M5Chart, etc.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:55 b685e354035749d8a16039f9aa820e6d
msgid "Available Fonts"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:57 bb4f70ade78849899c8d5ff28e7f7d46
