#: ../../source/m5ui/index.rst:101 229c91494e3c4a70970a1c17d148b66f
msgid ""
"``M5.Lcd.drawString()`` / ``M5.Widgets`` Chinese/Japanese/Korean text -> "
"``M5.Lcd.FONTS.Alibaba*24``"
msgstr ""

